    <description><![CDATA[Dependencies is a rewrite of the legacy software Dependency Walker which was shipped along Windows SDKs, but whose development stopped around 2006. Dependencies can help Windows developers troubleshooting their dll load dependencies issues.

## Package parameters
- `/InstallDir` - Installation directory, by default Chocolatey tools directory.
Example: `choco install dependencies --params "/InstallDir:C:\your\install\path"`

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is 
out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and
let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.]]></description>
